{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@discardableResult"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"onNotifyVersion"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"ConnectFlags","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV"},{"kind":"text","text":" = ConnectFlags(0), "},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"@escaping"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"ApplicationRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14ApplicationRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ApplicationRef"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV","text":"ParamSpecRef","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Flags"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"flags"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The signal handler to call","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Run the given callback whenever the ","type":"text"},{"code":"notifyVersion","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" signal is emitted"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"handler"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to "},{"code":"g_object_set_property()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" results","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when they explicitly call "},{"code":"g_object_notify()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"g_signal_connect()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" call, like this:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(C Language Example):"}]},{"code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"C"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is important to note that you must use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","tex